      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i've been looking at the network traffic on my machine since the last windows update and something is seriously wrong. the telemetry outbound is massive, way more than just \"diagnostic data.\" it looks like it's actually scraping memory heaps during idle time. have you seen anything about these specific recent updates having some kind of hidden payload or deeper surveillance function?",
